  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a grill or grill pan to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Season the beef patties with salt and black pepper.",
    "Add the high heat cooking oil to the preheated grill or grill pan.",
    "Sear the beef patties for 4 minutes per side.",
    "Assemble the sandwiches by spreading peppercorn sauce on the double-rise-bread.",
    "Add the beef patties, muenster cheese, pickle slices, and arugula to the sandwiches.",
    "Place the sandwiches under the broiler for 2 minutes to melt the cheese.",
    "Remove the sandwiches from the oven and let them cool for a minute.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
